						               													<description>Oh no! The sorcerer Darkthony has kidnapped our teacher, Blue Hat, and is keeping him captive in his evil Castle. Darkthony and his minions are on a frantic search for the seven powerful mega-crystals that will allow them to dominate the Bat Archipelago. Can we complete our quest and use our magical powers to save Blue Hat from the hands of Darkthony? He must be stopped!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Alchemical Crystal Quest is a cooperative fantasy board game featuring a campaign of ten missions. Players win the game if they complete all the missions&amp;mdash;each of which is a chapter in their quest. Players take the roles of alchemist magician apprentices on an adventure to discover the complete history of the Bat Archipelago and to save their alchemy teacher from the hands of the evil sorcerer Darkthony.&amp;#10; During the game, wizards search for keys, acquire magical artifacts, and spend crystals to upgrade their weapons. Wizards can change their size, ride magical pets, and engage in dice-rolling battles using weapon cards and spell cards. In some chapters, wizards will move onto special aerial tiles as they fly to the sky for flight-fight missions. Players create spells using combinations of colored crystals to equip their wizards with special abilities and magic attacks to fight their enemies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you succeed in completing all the chapters of your Quest and rescue Blue Hat, you will win the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Alchemical Crystal Quest features cartoon-style character miniatures for wizards, enemies, and magical pets. This game is for 1 to 4 players, and playtime is 40 to 120 minutes, depending on the mission.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
